title: Hour 1 – The Carson Wentz Trade Was A Win For Both Sides!
itunes:title: Hour 1 – The Carson Wentz Trade Was A Win For Both Sides!
description:
Jason Smith and Doug Gottlieb sit in for Dan Patrick and explain why they are optimistic for both the Eagles and Colts after completing a trade involving Carson Wentz. The guys talk question how long LeBron James’ can continue to play at such a high level and claim that the Steelers are forcing Ben Roethlisberger into retirement.
